      "rationale": "Simulation protocol documented in a formal simulation plan reviewed by an independent analyst. Boundary condition application, material assignment, and contact definition steps verified by peer review. Input deck independently reproduced by a second analyst with results within 0.3% of original. Gradation 2 achieved: documented simulation plan with independent peer review of model setup."
